id: pm-3y56
title: Single-source Plan workflow examples across plugin docs
description: "Duplicate audit 2026-05-22: Plan workflow examples are repeated across plugins/pm-claude/skills/pm-planner/SKILL.md:114-143, plugins/pm-codex/skills/pm-native/SKILL.md:59-75, and plugins/pm-claude/commands/pm-planner.md:53-69. The snippets describe pm_plan purpose and JSON lifecycle examples for create/add-step/update/complete/decision/approve/materialize/show/resume, but diverge by harness, included subcommands, and example fields. Closed pm-aqat exposed Plan workflow surfaces but does not track deduplicating copied plugin examples."
type: Chore
status: closed
priority: 3
tags[4]: dedup,docs,plan,plugins
